727814f-a.title: Queens: Queens Boulevard - 64th Road
727814f-a.text:
WQueens Boulevard, at the S.W. corner of 64th Road,
showing the home and hot houses of A.F. Schrader of 1909.
Part of the house and greenhouses stand in the path of the
1proposed 64th Road, which is shown being cut through.
P. L. Sperr  June 4, 1927
